    • loadLevel

      public static Level loadLevel(String filename) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException
      Loads serialized level object from given file.
      Parameters:
      filename - name of file with level object.
      Returns:
      loaded level.
      Throws:
      IOException - object can't be read from file.
      ClassNotFoundException - class of the level object can't be found.

    • saveLevel

      public static void saveLevel(Level level, String name)

      Parameters:
      level - object to serialize.
      name - name of the level object.

    • loadPlayer

      Returns:
      loaded player.
      Throws:
